      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and let me tell you\u2014it is in stunning, like-new condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. This beauty is looking for its next adventure, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. You\u2019ve really gotta see this one in person!",
