    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered masterpiece. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, this unit features a reinforced rear subframe and a documented dual-VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains taut, retaining its original suspension geometry and bushings for a precise, analog driving experience. Finished in pristine Carbon Black, the exterior exhibits zero imperfections, while the interior retains its factory matte finish. A turnkey collector-grade vehicle with a comprehensive service dossier.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
