    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presented in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, glass-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and factory-fresh, still carrying that new-car scent without a hint of wear on the bolsters or carpets. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the engine bay is pristine, reflecting a life of rigorous, no-expense-spared maintenance. With a comprehensive service history and zero mechanical imperfections, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. It is, without hyperbole, the finest example currently available on the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
